{"tid":1391952,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"(超合作運動) 渣車既巴絲入","createTime":"2019-07-31T14:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T15:17:07.000Z","uid":275380,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bd8f607e12b973fcfa8a801b24fd841c58e1bf0b","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:58:22.000Z","msg":"小弟係長期CD-ROM，最近先開AC, 不喜勿插<br />\n<br />\n相信大家渣車都成日遇過，啲工程撚成日封路（TTA, Temporary traffic Arrangement)  ，唔係封快線就封慢線，<br />\n成日Ｄ行車線就三收二，二收一，有啲人就話阻路可恥乜乜乜，拿，路爛就要整返好，岩既。<br />\n但有無發現黎黎去去，做路既都係果幾間公司，例如：昭hing,  Wai金, 順Yuen 等等。<br />\n<br />\n呢Ｄ公司既老細都好多公職架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如Wellcome既就係政協，順Yuen就係中華總商會會董咁<br />\n大家都愛國愛港，不用分得那麼細，拆爛河痴百歲磚咁叻叻，梗係想佢再做好Ｄ啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先封路呢，就要根據一本野，叫<strong>道路工程的照明、標誌及防護工作守則</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GP4j31t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGP4j31t.jpg&h=4f806f9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyd.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Fpublications_and_publicity%2Fpublications%2Ftechnical_document%2Fcode_of_practice%2Findex.html&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=8cbeaf71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hyd.gov.hk/tc/publications_and_publicity/publications/technical_document/code_of_practice/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n咁呢本野就詳細講述左封路既程序，點封法，燈，筒既間距咁<br />\n<br />\n當渣車可見到有封路前首先就係可以見到掘路，收窄同封link<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ow4Hf3B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOw4Hf3B.jpg&h=5e4d3562&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n通常於快速公路見到呢三款牌，下方都有＂接近危險地點標誌的距離字牌＂如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uqcYyUW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuqcYyUW.png&h=10c8c902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常呢Ｄ標誌牌都係寫住300,200,100或600,400,200<br />\n跟住再行前就會見到開始封路，呢啲路牌九成都會綁係路燈度，而路燈既間距為 30-40m，計計ＬＣＭ定ＨＣＦ就知每塊牌既間距係無可能係岩。<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係掘路，收窄同封link既實際樣子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/G2OdnV1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2OdnV1.jpg&h=3314236a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完左距離字牌就到封路既斜頭，公路既車速限制有唔同既長度，而呢個位置好大機會唔夠長，而道路工程終止牌則 經常被消失或缺左一邊<br />\n<br />\n<strong>楔形路段</strong>（斜頭）現實既樣：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZXQ9Ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZXQ9Ed.jpg&h=8936e3bc&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n參考表，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">封路愈寬，斜頭愈長，衰梗</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBYQqO3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBYQqO3.jpg&h=752c0305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而<span style=\"color: orange;\">雪糕筒間距</span>又係一個好有趣既切入位<br />\n<br />\n楔形路段及臨時改道路線邊緣&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2米&mdash;</span></strong><br />\n一般的<span style=\"font-size: large;\">楔形引入路段</span></span>，或在並非沿著現有行車綫邊緣的臨時改道行車綫兩旁。<br />\n1米&mdash;<br />\n在實施交通管制措施時成45度角的楔形引入路段，或在楔形引出路段。<br />\n1米&mdash;<br />\n佔用車路並與車路毗鄰的臨時行人路邊緣。<br />\n沿著現有行車綫的邊緣&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3米</span></span>&mdash;在車速限制每小時最高不超過<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">50</span></span>公里的路上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9米</span></span></span>&mdash;在車速限制每小時<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">70公里至80公里</span></span>的路上，或在車速限制超過每小時80公里的道路的急彎及近<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">連接路之處。</span></span>（當道路危險警告燈需要根據第4.35段的規定放置時，警告燈須放置在用作標示邊界的圓筒中間，並須安裝在附加的圓筒上，令道路使用者可每隔<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.5米</span></span>看到一個圓筒，並每隔一個圓筒看到一盞警告燈。）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">18米</span></span>&mdash;在車速限制<span style=\"color: violet;\">超過每小時80公里</span>的道路或快速公路，<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但在急彎或近連接路的道路</span></span>除外。（當道路危險警告燈需要根據第4.35段的規定放置時，警告燈須放置在用作標示邊界的圓筒中間，並須安裝在附加的圓筒上，令道路使用者可每隔<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">9米</span></span>看到一個圓筒，並可每隔一個圓筒看到一盞警告燈。）<br />\n<br />\n因為夜晚會加閃燈所以間距會唔同左，呢個有Ｄ複雜同煩，即係咁：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FFnd8da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFFnd8da.jpg&h=b629ae04&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咪就係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔夠囉</span><br />\n<br />\n所以如果封路封得衰係真係會死人架，google 一下偉kim就知真係修橋補路無屍骸，為人為己，如果發現佢封路封到有<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即時危險</span></span>，例如<strong>灣心起斜頭</strong>，Ｄ箭咀燈牌唔識閃或<strong>覺得</strong>暗，閃燈唔夠閃等等<br />\n可以致電９９９處理（如果打得通的話），清淅報出路段方向位置，記緊拎報案篇號跟進，相信交通部會很感激你的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果係非緊急而又想我地既愛國愛港人士再做好啲既<br />\n可用１８２３ａｐｐ，夠熟ＣＯＰ可以直接打去傾計，暫時１８２３係呢啲層面仲係有效既。由於封路都幾複雜，所以小弟做個簡單既 template，大家可以copy低做demo，附件是旦cap張影到條封路既車cam相，入晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係demo：<br />\n<br />\n本人支持政府依法施政，在XXXX年XX月XX日，於XX公路近XXX段往XX方向，發現有工程在公路上，不知道是什麼部門的，但啲工程車寫住 昭hing/ Wai金/ 順Yuen 咁，我經過時見到<br />\n<br />\n自選可多項：<br />\n&mdash;　雪糕筒好疏，明明xx km應該要 X米一個既 (透露自己係識既,明玩, 你咪試下唔跟進囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n&mdash;　斜頭雪糕筒好疏／唔夠密，明明。。。<br />\n&mdash;　閃燈好暗／閃燈唔迫識閃／無閃燈<br />\n&mdash;　箭咀燈唔識著／唔識閃／唔夠光／唔係箭咀<br />\n&mdash;　（如有，不過成日發生）工程車於封路內突然駛出，嚇到其他駕駛者（１８２３／９９９）<br />\n&mdash;　Ｄ指示牌擺度錯晒，誤導駕駛者，咁攪法真係好危險！<br />\n&mdash;　Ｄ人係封路做野唔戴安全帽／反光衣（如有）<br />\n&mdash;　剪草Ｄ碎彈晒出行車線<br />\n&mdash;　阻路可恥阻住我去返工<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"c88f231f49fc3f6afcfeb5b511cde1934b3b5f22","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dfa3bbc668539d9d19a55356418d9c79aff44e","tid":1391952,"uid":36095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做個良好公民<br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，大家一齊齊心舉報，警察係時候要做野"},{"pid":"c32e4c49e9b4e3a1d4faea0ab81e21403fbe2cc9","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86dfa3bbc668539d9d19a55356418d9c79aff44e","tid":1391952,"uid":36095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做個良好公民<br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，大家一齊齊心舉報，警察係時候要做野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"真心想佢地做好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be9a87bd40cd476b86b6ea583f95b2476d7ad97","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:08:35.000Z","msg":"建築工友要平平安安回家嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8353c946c58012060459ab71e71f7649d6917a1","tid":1391952,"uid":36095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c32e4c49e9b4e3a1d4faea0ab81e21403fbe2cc9","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"86dfa3bbc668539d9d19a55356418d9c79aff44e","tid":1391952,"uid":36095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:07:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做個良好公民<br />\n<br />\n馬路如虎口，大家一齊齊心舉報，警察係時候要做野"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"真心想佢地做好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:08:37.000Z","msg":"總之係唔係都即時危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ea8bef91e04a35da295e19c5e47fceda14496a","tid":1391952,"uid":80234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:12:41.000Z","msg":"技術文好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼續發掘更多超合作運動"},{"pid":"c2e209c4f341e5144aa06b55457054edcc3c8f0a","tid":1391952,"uid":275380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:34:34.000Z","msg":"其實999之後可以再1823<br />\n因999係警察跟進<br />\n而1823就會落左封路果個deptment再入9 contractor<br />\n<br />\nWhy not both"},{"pid":"1b7c0754cc0ded082ed02073502834277abc06b7","tid":1391952,"uid":289867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"行家師兄識嘢<br />\n<br />\n長知識了<br />\n<br />\n幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcd8f03cb831c846514406b5650f2b0fa746261b","tid":1391952,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:43:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"279953659e6e21761cf0acf42e93a2857fd9fb22","tid":1391952,"uid":115977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ffFLfvr